title: John Pizzarelli Discography {mp3} by Dreher
description:
John Pizzarelli Discography mp3 by Dreher

HO HO HO!!! Merry Christmas!!! This is my gift to all of you!!!

It took me a looooooooot of hard work to put all this mp3 discography together. I realized that there was no torrent available with all the John Pizzarelli discography.

Well there are still a few albums missing like I'm Hip )Please Don't Tell My Father) and some others, but this is all I could put together:

(1987) Live at The Vineyard Theatre [& Bucky Pizzarelli]
(1990) My Blue Heaven
(1992) All of Me
(1993) Naturally
(1994) Dear Mr. Cole
(1994) New Standards
(1994) The Best of John Pizzarelli - I Like Jersey Best
(1996) After Hours
(1996) Let's Share Christmas
(1996) One Night With You
(1997) Our Love Is Here to Stay
(1998) Meets The Beatles
(1999) Harry Allen Meets John Pizzarelli Trio
(1999) PS Mr. Cole
(2000) Brazil
(2000) Kisses in the Rain
(2000) Let There Be Love
(2002) The Rare Delight of You with The George Shearing Quintet
(2003) Live At Birdland [2CDs]
